&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Strategy &amp;amp; Infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design and execution of Elemental’s organizational data strategy, including the portfolio annual shareholder survey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and continuously improve centralized data infrastructure, primarily within HubSpot and Airtable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve the organization&#39;s CRM architecture, including stakeholder engagement, pipeline tracking, and reporting systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to leverage AI tools, automate workflows, integrate emerging technologies, and improve organizational efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
